
# Installation of Spring cli and Spring cloud cli

## Installation of Spring Cli using OSX Homebrew

If you are on a Mac and using Homebrew, all you need to do to install the Spring Boot CLI is:

```
brew tap pivotal/tap
brew install springboot
```

For installation using other sources,
> https://docs.spring.io/spring-boot/docs/current/reference/html/getting-started-installing-spring-boot.html

Homebrew will install spring to /usr/local/bin.

## Installation of Spring Cloud Cli using Spring Cli

```
spring install org.springframework.cloud:spring-cloud-cli:1.4.0.RELEASE
```

## Launch Stub runner using the configuration specified in stubrunner.yml
```
cd stub-runner-config
spring cloud stubrunner
```